targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  profile_picture_url
FROM "UserProfiles"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  media_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  followers_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  follows_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY insight_date DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  sum(like_count)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  sum(comments_count)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

select sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) 
from (select distinct(mi.media_id), max(mi.saved) as totalSaved
from "MediaInsights" mi, "Media" m
where saved is not null and mi.media_id = m.media_id and m.instagram_business_account = $user_id
group by mi.media_id) as reqSaved

WITH mediaCounts as (
SELECT
  sum(like_count) as likeCount,
  sum(comments_count) as commentsCount
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
), savedCount as (
select sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) as totSaved
from (select distinct(media_id), max(saved) as totalSaved
from "MediaInsights" mi
where saved is not null
group by media_id) as reqSaved)

SELECT
  cast ((mediaCounts.likeCount + mediaCounts.commentsCount + savedCount.totSaved) as float) / followers_count as engRate
FROM "UserInsights", mediaCounts, savedCount
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER by insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  media_type,
  count(media_id) as total
FROM
  "Media"
group by media_type
order by total desc

SELECT
  cast (sum(like_count) as float) / count(media_id)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  cast (sum(comments_count) as float) / count(media_id)
FROM "Media"
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id

select cast (sum(reqSaved.totalSaved) as float) / count(reqSaved.totalMedia)
from (select distinct(mi.media_id), max(mi.saved) as totalSaved, count(m.media_id) as totalMedia
from "MediaInsights" mi, "Media" m
where saved is not null and mi.media_id = m.media_id and m.instagram_business_account = $user_id
group by mi.media_id) as reqSaved

WITH engTotal as (
select sum(engAll) as eng
from (
	select max(engagement) as engAll
	from "MediaInsights" mi
	where mi.media_id in (select media_id from "Media" order by "timestamp" desc limit 20)
	group by mi.media_id 
	) as engList
)

SELECT
  cast (engTotal.eng as float)*100/20 / followers_count as engRate
FROM "UserInsights", engTotal
WHERE
  instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER by insight_date desc
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  followers_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  likes_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
  and instagram_business_account = $user_id

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  follows_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  media_count
FROM "UserInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  email_contacts 
FROM "UserDetailedInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  impressions,
  reach
FROM "UserDetailedInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  profile_views 
FROM "UserDetailedInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  reach 
FROM "UserDetailedInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  text_message_clicks 
FROM "UserDetailedInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  insight_date AS "time",
  website_clicks 
FROM "UserDetailedInsights"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(insight_date)
ORDER BY 1
